content:
Create a Contact and Use a Formula
An Omnistudio Data Mapper Load creates a record in the Salesforce Contact object. A formula checks whether the contact is over 18 years old: if so, a custom Authorized field is set to true.

Create a Contact for an Existing Account
The following example of an Omnistudio Data Mapper Load creates a record in the Salesforce Contact object. A link to an Account object record with a specific Id ensures that the new Contact is related to that Account.

Omnistudio Data Mapper Load Examples demonstrate formulas and object relationships.
title: Omnistudio Data Mapper Load Examples
